<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Trucking company database manager</title>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charseet=UTF-8" />
    <style type="text/css">
        .header {
            background-color: #E5C821;
            padding: 15px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .caption {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
            color: white;
            background-color: #A0A0A0;
            padding: 25px;
        }
        th, td {
            height: 30px;
            font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
            border-style: solid;
            border-color: #A0A0A0;
            border-width: 1px;
        }
        table {
            width: 100%;
            font-size: 14px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="header">
    <h2 style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: white; font-size: 400%;">
        Trucking company database manager
    </h2>
</div>
<div>
    <table>
        <caption class="caption"><b>ИНФОРМАЦИЯ О РЕМОНТАХ ДЛЯ {{transportInfo}}, ИСПОЛЬЗОВАНО: {{sparePartsNum}}шт., ЗАПЧАСТЬ: "{{sparePart}}"</b></caption>
        <tr>
            <th>ID</th>
            <th>Стоимость</th>
            <th>Принято</th>
            <th>Возвращено</th>
            <th>Запчасть</th>
            <th>Бригада</th>
            <th>Транспорт</th>
        </tr>
        {{#repairs}}
            <tr>
                <td>{{repId}}</td>
                <td>{{cost}}</td>
                <td>{{received}}</td>
                <td>{{returned}}</td>
                <td>{{sparePart}}</td>
                <td>{{brigade.brigadeId}}</td>
                <td>{{transport.id}}</td>
            </tr>
        {{/repairs}}
    </table>
</div>
</body>
</html>